e with 3 implementation tasks and 2 verification items (all unchecked)\n\n---\n\n## 3. Design Documents Related to AR-037 and ST-3\n\n### AR-037 Specific Files (in `changes/AR-037/`)\n\n| File | Path | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| **proposal.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-037/proposal.md` | PCAP analyzer example application proposal. Module: example, Language: Python, Size: M. Covers example script, auxiliary files, SDK API coverage, architecture, impact analysis, alternatives considered. |\n| **design.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-037/design.md` | 578-line detailed design: architecture diagrams, data structures (JSON result format, CLI args, env vars), interfaces (main entry point, core analysis function, embedded scapy script, optional tshark), error handling, testing strategy, usage examples, README content. |\n| **delta-spec.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md` | 17-line placeholder template (empty Additions/Modifications/Deletions sections). |\n| **tasks.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-037/tasks.md` | 12-line placeholder with 3 unchecked implementation tasks and 2 unchecked verification items. |\n\n### Root-Level AR-037 Documents\n\n| File | Path | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| **delta-spec.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` | 191-line detailed delta spec covering CLI argument parsing, PCAP file upload, analysis script generation (summary/top-talkers/dns modes), script execution, result download, output formatting, session lifecycle. |\n| **.sdd_prompt.md** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` | 465-line SDD (Software Design Document) prompt that includes the full python-sdk design.md and spec.md as context for generating the AR-037 design. |\n\n### ST-3 References\nST-3 refers to the \"Design Complete\" stage. It is referenced in the header of tasks.md files for AR-002 through AR-036. For example, AR-012 through AR-036 state: `> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed`.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Example Module Structure\n\nThe `example/` directory contains a single subdirectory:\n\n```\nexample/\n  pcap-analyzer/\n    pcap_analyzer.py        # Main FastAPI application (321 lines)\n    requirements.txt        # Dependencies (FastAPI, uvicorn, LangChain, LangGraph, paramiko)\n    Dockerfile              # uv-based container image\n    deployment.yaml         # Kubernetes Deployment manifest\n    README.md               # Documentation (124 lines)\n    tests/\n      test_pcap_analyzer.py  # Endpoint and config tests (181 lines)\n      test_agents.py         # Agent building/invocation tests (170 lines)\n      test_sandbox_runner.py # SandboxRunner unit tests (185 lines)\n```\n\n### Architecture of the Example\nThe pcap-analyzer is a **FastAPI web service** (not a CLI script) that uses LangChain/LangGraph ReAct agents for:\n1. **Plan**: Generate a Python analysis script via LLM\n2. **Execute**: Run the script in an AgentCube sandbox via `SandboxRunner`\n3. **Repair**: Auto-fix failed scripts (up to 2 retries)\n4. **Report**: Generate a human-readable report via LLM\n\nKey components:\n- `SandboxRunner` -- wraps `CodeInterpreterClient` with `upload_file`, `upload_bytes`, `run`, `stop`\n- `build_planner_agent` / `build_reporter_agent` -- LangGraph ReAct agent factories\n- `_analyze_with_retries` -- orchestration with retry logic\n- `POST /analyze` endpoint -- accepts PCAP file upload or server-side path\n\n---\n\n## 5. Python Example Applications\n\n### A. `example/pcap-analyzer/` (described above)\n- **Type**: FastAPI + LangChain/LangGraph web service\n- **Files**: 9 files (source + tests + config)\n- **Dependencies**: fastapi, uvicorn, langchain-*, langgraph-*, paramiko, python-multipart\n\n### B. `cmd/cli/examples/` -- CLI Agent Examples\n\n| Example | Path | Description |\n|---------|------|-------------|\n| **hello-agent** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/` | Minimal example: `main.py` is just `print(\"Hello from AgentCube!\")` (3 lines). Also has `agent_metadata.yaml` and `requirements.txt`. |\n| **math-agent** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/` | Simple math expression evaluator using `eval()` (20 lines). Has `agent_metadata.yaml` and `requirements.txt`. |\n| **java-agent** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/examples/java-agent/` | Java example with Maven project structure, `App.java`, `pom.xml`, Eclipse project files, and `agent_metadata.yaml`. |\n\n### C. Python SDK (`python-sdk/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/`\n- **Public exports**: `CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient`\n- **Source files**:\n  - `agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - `agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - `agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - `agentcube/utils/http.py`, `utils.py`, `log.py`\n- **Tests**: `test_code_interpreter.py`, `test_agent_runtime.py`, `test_control_plane.py`, `test_data_plane.py`, `test_utils.py`, `test_exceptions.py`, `test_imports.py`, `conftest.py`\n\n### D. Dify Plugin Integration (`integrations/dify-plugin/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/integrations/dify-plugin/`\n- **Python files**: `main.py`, `provider/agentcube.py`, `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`, tests\n- **Purpose**: Dify platform plugin that delegates to `agentcube.CodeInterpreterClient`\n\n### E. CLI Tool (`cmd/cli/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/`\n- **Python files**: CLI main (`agentcube/cli/main.py`), runtime operations (build, pack, publish, invoke, status), services (AgentCube provider, K8s provider, Docker service, metadata service), models, and extensive tests\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28504a68bffeHei36u3OtoS7r3","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775884786033,"end":1775884941865}}}}
